---
title: Mexican Street Corn Pasta with Bell Pepper, Jalapeño & Pepper Jack
description: In Mexico, you can stroll down a sunny street and spot colorful elote, or corn on the cob, charring on a grill cart, the smell of fragrant spices, cheeses, and herbs wafting through the breeze. Now, thanks to a few hearty additions, you can turn this street snack into a filling dinner! Bell pepper, jalapeño, and paprika infuse this pasta with not-too-spicy chili flavor, while sweet corn and penne balance the heat. Then pasta is swirled with cream sauce, cream cheese, and pepper jack for a dreamy take on a traditional fave—right from the comfort of your own casa!
